### 1. Register (pas de token JWT, juste le token d'activation)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company_name": "HireBox Corp",
  "website": "https://hirebox.com",
  "email": "contact@hirebox.com",
  "password": "Secure@2024!"
}

###

### 2. Login sans activation (doit retourner 401)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "contact@hirebox.com",
  "password": "Secure@2024!"
}

###

### 3. Activer le compte (colle le token du register)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/activate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "b31f1566-eb0a-45b1-816c-69f2d2bcaeb1"
}

###

### 4. Login après activation (doit retourner les tokens JWT)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "contact@hirebox.com",
  "password": "Secure@2024!"
}